Description

A text entry having dialog or list containing items for insertion into an entry widget, for instance a list of words for completion of a text entry.

Mapped to

  • AT-SPI: ROLE_AUTOCOMPLETE
  • ATK: NSAccessibilityComboBoxRole
  • UA: @"AXRuler"
  • MSAA/IA2: ROLE_SYSTEM_COMBOBOX

Used by

  • XUL: <textbox type="autocomplete"/>
